      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BALI UNLEASHED (2) is a talented type and proved too strong last time to win by one length at this track in a handy 30.67 beating Lektra Sting. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and three minor placings to her credit. Great chance to get the job done again. TODD KEEPING (1) scored well last start as odds-on favourite by 5.5 lengths at Gawler in a handy 22.58 beating Crazed. Has the coveted inside box and goes well at this distance. The form from his last run is stacking up nicely. Can make it back-to-back wins. LIL REX (3) is a well performed dog who recorded his 11th career win last time out at Angle Park (43.05). Smart beginner who should take advantage of the low draw. Sure to be thereabouts. STATUE OF TIME (8) placed last time and cannot be ignored.",
